Updated for 2019.

v1.20181021

    - autogenerate META.json file (Mohammad S Anwar, GH PR #7)
    - remove Module::Build build dependency to make installation easier

Remove Module::Build dependency.

This makes installation easier and faster, especially on new Perl
installations. That's fewer non-core dependencies.

I wish I'd thought of this years ago.
Update Changes for next release.
Auto generate META.json using dzil plugin [MetaJSON].
